message.body: News alert: Ian Eckerts new wife is pregnant. What is wrong with me? Why does this still occupy some strange, horrible corner of my heart?
Time to listen to Jeff Buckley and deactivate Facebook.
Let yourself feel sad tonight if u need to
Or even for a couple days
But remember those emotions, no matter how intense they, don't deserve power
But remember those emotions, no matter how intense they FEEL, don't deserve power
Thanks soafs. Today is better--barely a thought now. It's just so crazy how memories work. I hope you are doing well!!!
I'm coming to Philly for new years will you be around
I think so. No plans otherwise yet.
